//! Pub same-bare-name type fixture (narrow layout). Exports a public `Gadget`
//! record whose sole field is an `i8`. Its sibling `hew::widgetpub64` exports a
//! public `Gadget` of the same bare name carrying an `i64` — a divergent
//! layout. Used by the published-bare-name ambiguity oracle: an importer that
//! opts `Gadget` in from THIS module (`::{ Gadget }`) and plain-imports the
//! sibling must resolve a bare `Gadget` to THIS module's identity (the
//! published owner), not error ambiguous and not bind the sibling's layout.

/// Narrow `Gadget`: a single `i8` field.
pub type Gadget {
    v: i8;
}
